fields.name: AssociatedResourceIds
fields.description: The list of resource IDs for the other Microsoft.NetworkCloud resources that have attached this network.

fields.name: ClusterId
fields.description: The resource ID of the Network Cloud cluster this L3 network is associated with.

fields.name: DetailedStatus
fields.description: The more detailed status of the L3 network.

fields.name: DetailedStatusMessage
fields.description: The descriptive message about the current detailed status.

fields.name: HybridAksClustersAssociatedIds
fields.description: Field Deprecated. These fields will be empty/omitted. The list of Hybrid AKS cluster resource IDs that are associated with this L3 network.

fields.name: HybridAksIPamEnabled
fields.description: Field Deprecated. The field was previously optional, now it will have no defined behavior and will be ignored. The indicator of whether or not to disable IPAM allocation on the network attachment definition injected into the Hybrid AKS Cluster.

fields.name: HybridAksPluginType
fields.description: Field Deprecated. The field was previously optional, now it will have no defined behavior and will be ignored. The network plugin type for Hybrid AKS.

fields.name: IPAllocationType
fields.description: The type of the IP address allocation, defaulted to "DualStack".

fields.name: IPv4ConnectedPrefix
fields.description:
The IPV4 prefix (CIDR) assigned to this L3 network. Required when the IP allocation type
is IPV4 or DualStack.

fields.name: IPv6ConnectedPrefix
fields.description:
The IPV6 prefix (CIDR) assigned to this L3 network. Required when the IP allocation type
is IPV6 or DualStack.

fields.name: InterfaceName
fields.description: The default interface name for this L3 network in the virtual machine. This name can be overridden by the name supplied in the network attachment configuration of that virtual machine.

fields.name: L3IsolationDomainId
fields.description: The resource ID of the Network Fabric l3IsolationDomain.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the L3 network.

fields.name: VirtualMachinesAssociatedIds
fields.description: Field Deprecated. These fields will be empty/omitted. The list of virtual machine resource IDs, excluding any Hybrid AKS virtual machines, that are currently using this L3 network.

fields.name: Vlan
fields.description: The VLAN from the l3IsolationDomain that is used for this network.
